{"tid":451932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[奇人奇事]大家聽過最離譜最好笑嘅事係咩？？","createTime":"2017-10-29T16:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T16:46:10.000Z","uid":32792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9b97cb7e2ed74cc81eb791d74c24aa5fb0f642","tid":451932,"uid":32792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日有對都唔算年輕嘅男女黎我做野間餐廳到食野<br />\n咁佢地叫左幾樣野la其中叫左個醬油蟹set<br />\n咁佢叫得我地就當然上俾佢la<br />\n我一上個女人就掂一掂隻蟹問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜生嘅<br />\n我就冇點理翻翻去<br />\n之後到我大佬岀去就俾對男女捉住黎問<br />\n詳細我都唔太清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我大佬一翻黎同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條友唔食生野你攞去焗熟佢俾佢地食la<br />\n我即刻nick young.gif<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醬油蟹攞去焗真係新奇又有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5101425532289d8e886be548ce414bdfac3edc7f","tid":451932,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"園林四不像"},{"pid":"186c4495ab707d791354ef6278127b0de2e1102b","tid":451932,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"Xdd"},{"pid":"7a055ae4454c73357e11d2a0450c34d1771c77a0","tid":451932,"uid":32792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3383e8e5bf687e95318d636a05b1564c3367a85","tid":451932,"uid":